WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.083 --> 00:00:03.384 size:50% line:10%
♪ "Is It Supposed"
by Hudson Mohawke ♪

00:00:03.384 --> 00:00:06.719 size:60% line:10%
Not everyone holds
their iPhone like this.

00:00:06.719 --> 00:00:08.939 size:55% line:10%
We need more options.

00:00:08.939 --> 00:00:12.160 size:78% line:79%
- I have tingling
in my fingers and sharp pains.

00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:14.799 size:81% line:79%
- I don't have big enough hands
to actually hold my phone

00:00:14.799 --> 00:00:15.974 size:68% line:85%
and type at the same time.

00:00:15.974 --> 00:00:18.859 size:76% line:79%
- If you can't grip it right,
you're going to drop it.

00:00:18.859 --> 00:00:23.513 size:81% line:79%
- It is important to ask people
what they need.

00:00:23.513 --> 00:00:27.410 size:52% line:10%
And I started making
phone cases by hand.

00:00:27.410 --> 00:00:29.534 size:71% line:79%
I'm going to put
all these out on the table.

00:00:29.534 --> 00:00:31.199 size:63% line:79%
- We're going to turn it
upside down.

00:00:31.199 --> 00:00:32.398 size:60% line:85%
- That's going to fall.

00:00:32.398 --> 00:00:34.193 size:2% position:88%,middle line:10%
♪

00:00:34.193 --> 00:00:39.230 size:81% line:79%
- This specific design came out
of multiple conversations

00:00:39.230 --> 00:00:43.560 size:63% line:79%
with people of all kinds
of disabilities.

00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:45.140 size:65% line:85%
- This feels real stable.

00:00:45.140 --> 00:00:47.820 size:84% line:79%
- And it had the grooves where
you could put your finger in it.

00:00:47.820 --> 00:00:49.880 size:71% line:79%
- So I can flip it.
- It's very secure to hold.

00:00:49.880 --> 00:00:50.765 size:34% line:85%
- The colors.

00:00:50.765 --> 00:00:52.219 size:68% line:85%
- Wow, that's really bold.

00:00:52.219 --> 00:00:54.902 size:73% line:85%
- It claims its differences.

00:00:54.902 --> 00:00:57.793 size:42% line:79%
I love how proud
of itself it is.

00:00:57.793 --> 00:00:59.093 size:55% line:79%
- You should be proud
of yourself

00:00:59.093 --> 00:01:00.393 size:60% line:85%
and proud of your body.

00:01:00.393 --> 00:01:02.439 size:52% line:79%
- Accessibility
is also inclusivity,

00:01:02.439 --> 00:01:04.829 size:68% line:85%
and it makes us feel seen.

00:01:04.829 --> 00:01:05.992 size:63% line:85%
- So that's really cool.

